---
import Section from "../Section.astro";
---

<Section title="about" anchor="home">
  <div class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Software Engineer</p>
    <h1>Jose Miguel Navarro</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Backend software engineer focused on Node.js, TypeScript, API design, and
      scalable cloud architecture on AWS.
    </p>
    <div class="chips">
      <span>Node.js</span>
      <span>TypeScript</span>
      <span>AWS</span>
      <span>PostgreSQL</span>
      <span>Seoul</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="block">
    <p>
      I currently work at Criptan as a Software Engineer, building backend
      services with Node.js and TypeScript on event-driven AWS serverless
      infrastructure.
    </p>
    <p>
      I graduated from UPM (Madrid), specialized in distributed software and
      services, and have worked across fintech, developer platforms, and
      exchange products.
    </p>
    <p>
      My focus is building scalable and maintainable systems that align with
      business goals, from architecture and API implementation to shipping and
      iteration. You can explore my <a href="#projects">software projects</a>
      and <a href="#experience">work experience</a> below.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 0 10px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.11em;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--brand);
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .lead {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    max-width: 65ch;
  }
  .chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .chips span {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 6px 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .block {
    text-align: left;
  }
  .block p {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .block:not(:last-child) {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
</style>
